              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Titan Comics recently reissued the first three Dark Souls graphic novels in box set format, but you can already <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-1-3-Boxed-Set/dp/1787741494?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">save nearly 50% on the three-volume paperback set</a> at Amazon. Normally $50, the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-1-3-Boxed-Set/dp/1787741494?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dark Souls 1-3 Slipcase Set</a> is on sale for only $28.49.</p><div title="6523741 - Dark Souls Graphic Novel Box Set" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="2409" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6523741 - Dark Souls Graphic Novel Box Set" data-collection="">             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-1-3-Boxed-Set/dp/1787741494?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Dark-Souls-1-3-Boxed-Set\/dp\/1787741494?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-1-3-Boxed-Set/dp/1787741494?tag=gamespot-promos-20">Dark Souls Graphic Novel Box Set (Volumes 1-3)</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-1-3-Boxed-Set/dp/1787741494?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Dark-Souls-1-3-Boxed-Set\/dp\/1787741494?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-1-3-Boxed-Set/dp/1787741494?tag=gamespot-promos-20">Box Set - $28.49 (was $50) | Omnibus - $25 (was $35)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>The box set contains the first three graphic novels in the series--Dark Souls: Breath of Andolus, Dark Souls: Winters Spite, and Dark Souls: Legends of the Flame. In total, the three graphic novels clock in at 336 pages.</p><p>The Dark Souls graphic novel series features the aesthetic and some of the locales found in the popular From Software games, but this trio of books penned by George Mann and illustrated by Alan Quah are original tales with new characters and quests. Each paperback is filled with gorgeously grotesque art and come packaged in a new slipcase designed for this reissued collection.</p><p>Author George Mann has adapted multiple other major franchises into novels and comic books, including Star Wars, Doctor Who, Dragon Age, and Warhammer.</p><p>It's worth noting that these three graphic novels were previously compiled in <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-Collection-George-Mann/dp/1787737276?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dark Souls: The Complete Collection</a>, a 384-page paperback omnibus that also includes a prequel graphic novel titled The Age of Fire and the Tales of Ember short story anthology. The single-volume collection retails for $35, but is on sale for only $25 at Amazon.</p></div>                      </div><h3>Dark Souls Graphic Novels</h3><p>The latest entry in the Dark Souls graphic novel series, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-Willow-George-Mann/dp/1787731626?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Willow King</a>, released last August. You can find links to each individual volume below.</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-Collection-George-Mann/dp/1787737276?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dark Souls: The Complete Collection</a> -- $25 (<del>$35</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-Andolus-George-Mann/dp/178585366X?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dark Souls Vol. 1: The Breath of Andolus</a> -- $14 (<del>$18</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-Breath-Andolus-Artists/dp/1785861646?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dark Souls Vol. 1: The Breath of Andolus - Artist's Edition</a> -- $29</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-Winters-George-Mann/dp/1785853678?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dark Souls Vol. 2: Winter's Spite</a> -- $14 (<del>$18</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-Legends-Dan-Watters/dp/1785861662?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dark Souls Vol. 3: Legends of the Flame</a> -- $17 (<del>$18</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-Fire-Ryan-OSullivan/dp/1787731758?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dark Souls Vol. 4: The Age of Fire</a> -- $22</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dark-Souls-Willow-George-Mann/dp/1787731626?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dark Souls Vol. 5: The Willow King</a> -- $16 (<del>$18</del>)</li></ul><h3>Bloodborne Graphic Novels</h3><p>Titan Comics also adapted From Software's Bloodborne into a graphic novel series. The sixth volume in the series, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Bloodborne-Bleak-Dominion-Cullen-Bunn/dp/1787740633?tag=gamespot-promos-20&amp;tag=gamespot-buybutton-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Bleak Dominion</a>, released last summer and is on sale for only $10 at Amazon. Similarly, you can pick up a <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Bloodborne-1-3-Boxed-Set-Ales/dp/1787735338?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">budget-friendly box set</a> that matches the style of the newer Dark Souls set. </p><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Bloodborne-1-3-Boxed-Set-Ales/dp/1787735338?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Bloodborne Vol. 1-3 Box Set</a> -- $29 (<del>$50</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Bloodborne-Death-Sleep-Ales-Kot/dp/1785863444?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Bloodborne Vol. 1: The Death of Sleep</a> -- $13.59 (<del>$18</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Bloodborne-Vol-2-Healing-Thirst/dp/1785869531?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Bloodborne Vol. 2: The Healing Thirst</a> -- $15.62 (<del>$18</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Bloodborne-Song-Crows-Ales-Kot/dp/178773014X?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Bloodborne Vol. 3: A Song of Crows</a> -- $15.85 (<del>$18</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Bloodborne-4-Veil-Torn-Asunder/dp/1787730158?tag=gamespot-promos-20&amp;tag=gamespot-buybutton-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Bloodborne Vol. 4: The Veil Torn Asunder</a> -- $16.43 (<del>$18</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Bloodborne-Lady-Lanterns-Graphic-Novel/dp/1787735990?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Bloodborne Vol. 5: Lady of the Lanterns</a> -- $18</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Bloodborne-Bleak-Dominion-Cullen-Bunn/dp/1787740633?tag=gamespot-promos-20&amp;tag=gamespot-buybutton-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Bloodborne Vol. 6: The Bleak Dominion</a> -- $10 (<del>$18</del>)</li></ul><h3>Elden Ring Manga</h3><p>Meanwhile, From Software's latest hit, Elden Ring, has a comedy manga series that shows fans a different side of The Lands Between.</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Elden-Ring-Road-Erdtree-Vol/dp/1975364899?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Elden Ring: The Road to the Erdtree Volume 1 (Paperback)</a> -- $12 ($<del>13</del>) | Kindle - $7</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Elden-Ring-Road-Erdtree-Vol/dp/1975391144?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Elden Ring: The Road to the Erdtree Volume 2 (Paperback)</a> -- $12 (<del>$13</del>) | Kindle - $7</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Elden-Ring-Road-Erdtree-Vol/dp/1975396545?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow ">Elden Ring: The Road to the Erdtree Volume 3 (Paperback)</a> -- $10 (<del>$13</del>) | Kindle - $7</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Elden-Ring-Road-Erdtree-Vol/dp/B0D2WZ157R?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow ">Elden Ring: The Road to the Erdtree Volume 4 (Paperback)</a> -- $12 (<del>$13</del>) | Kindle - $7</li></ul><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/super-mario-world-lego-set-is-discounted-at-amazon-but-probably-not-for-long/1100-6525283/">Super Mario World Lego Set Is Discounted At Amazon, But Probably Not For Long</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/fortnite-festival-riffmaster-wireless-guitar-controller-gets-rare-discount/1100-6528970/">Fortnite Festival Riffmaster Wireless Guitar Controller Gets Rare Discount</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/save-25-on-donkey-kong-country-returns-hd-for-nintendo-switch/1100-6524388/">Save 25% On Donkey Kong Country Returns HD For Nintendo Switch</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/last-chance-to-grab-3-movies-on-4k-blu-ray-for-only-33-at-amazon/1100-6528683/">Last Chance To Grab 3 Movies On 4K Blu-Ray For Only $33 At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/final-fantasy-7-remake-ps5-reprint-restocked-at-amazon/1100-6528630/">Final Fantasy 7 Remake Physical Edition Gets PS5 Reprint - Snag It While You Can</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-2500-piece-legend-of-zelda-lego-set-is-now-available-at-amazon/1100-6523747/">The 2,500-Piece Legend Of Zelda Lego Set Is Now Available At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/mario-kart-lego-sets-are-available-now-check-out-all-six-in-the-launch-lineup/1100-6528603/">Mario Kart Lego Sets Are Available Now - Check Out All Six In The Launch Lineup</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/fortnite-lego-sets-launch-at-major-retailers-including-amazon-and-walmart/1100-6528629/">Fortnite Lego Sets Launch At Major Retailers, Including Amazon And Walmart</a></li>   </ul> </div>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
